Route 10 -- Gum Springs Church Road SW

Southeastern Chatham County

Date -- June 17, 2000
Time -- 5:15 EDT
Observers -- Sue Brady

NOTES

A hen Wild Turkey started things off -- also Whip-poor-wills!   Followed by record numbers of Northern Rough-winged Swallows and Blue-gray Gnatcatchers -- and some good warblers!
